.%20Swiss%20prosecutor%20Yves%20Bertossa%20stated%20that%20the%20family's%20yearly%20spending%20on%20their%20dog%20amounted%20to%208%2C584%20Swiss%20francs%20(%E2%82%B9%208%2C09%2C399)%2C%20whereas%20some%20staff%20allegedly%20worked%20up%20to%2018%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20for%20as%20little%20as%207%20Swiss%20francs%20(%E2%82%B9%20660)%20per%20day.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20The%20family%20allegedly%20confiscated%20the%20passports%20of%20their%20staff%20members%20from%20India%2C%20restricting%20their%20freedom%20to%20leave%20the%20premises%20without%20permission.%20This%20potentially%20constitutes%20human%20trafficking%20under%20Swiss%20law.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn3.%20The%20staff%20were%20paid%20in%20Indian%20currency%2C%20leaving%20them%20without%20money%20in%20Switzerland.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn4.%20Contracts%20for%20the%20staff%20reportedly%20did%20not%20specify%20working%20hours%20or%20days%20off%20but%20required%20them%20to%20be%20available%20as%20needed%20by%20the%20family.%20This%20lack%20of%20clarity%20contributed%20to%20the%20alleged%20exploitation%2C%20as%20per%20the%20prosecutor's%20arguments%20in%20court.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn5.%20The%20defence%20responded%20to%20accusations%2C%20saying%20they%20treated%20their%20staff%20with%20respect%20and%20provided%20them%20with%20accommodation%20and%20meals%20as%20part%20of%20their%20compensation.%20They%20pointed%20out%20the%20staff%20returned%20to%20work%20for%20the%20family%20repeatedly%2C%20which%20they%20argued%20showed%20that%20they%20were%20satisfied%20with%20their%20working%20conditions.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnRepresenting%20the%20Hindujas%2C%20Romain%20Jordan%20denied%20the%20allegations%2C%20saying%20the%20family%20was%20not%20directly%20involved%20in%20hiring%20or%20managing%20their%20staff.%20He%20accused%20prosecutors%20of%20bias%20against%20the%20billionaire%20family%2C%20stating%20that%20no%20other%20family%20would%20be%20treated%20this%20way.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnProsecutors%20are%20now%20asking%20for%20lengthy%20prison%20sentences%20for%20Prakash%20Hinduja%2C%20his%20wife%20Kamal%2C%20their%20son%20Ajay%20and%20his%20wife%20Namrata.%20They%20also%20want%20the%20family%20to%20pay%201%20million%20Swiss%20francs%20for%20court%20costs%20and%20set%20up%20a%203.5%20million%20francs%20compensation%20fund%20for%20the%20staff%20affected%2C%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fmaryroeloffs%2F2024%2F06%2F17%2Fbillionaire-hinduja-family-accused-of-confiscating-staff-passports-forcing-18-hour-work-days%2F%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718786760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fekal4go8_prakash-hinduja_625x300_19_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbillionaire-hinduja-family-faces-human-trafficking-charges-in-swiss-court-5-shocking-revelations-5921921%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hindujas%2C%20the%20wealthiest%20family%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20are%20facing%20trial%20in%20Geneva%20on%20accusations%20of%20human%20trafficking%20and%20exploiting%20staff%20at%20their%20Swiss%20villa%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20in%20Bloomberg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbillionaire-hinduja-family-faces-human-trafficking-charges-in-swiss-court-5-shocking-revelations-5921921%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbillionaire-hinduja-family-faces-human-trafficking-charges-in-swiss-court-5-shocking-revelations-5921921%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbillionaire-hinduja-family-faces-human-trafficking-charges-in-swiss-court-5-shocking-revelations-5921921%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bengali%20Actor%20Rituparna%20Sengupta%20Questioned%20In%20Alleged%20Corruption%20Case%22