%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20come%20to%20Nalanda%20within%2010%20days%20of%20taking%20oath%20for%20the%20third%20term.%20This%20is%20good%20luck.%20I%20also%20see%20this%20as%20a%20good%20omen%20in%20India's%20development%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeveloped%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20ancient%20university%20at%20Nalanda%2C%20the%20central%20university%20has%20two%20academic%20blocks%20with%2040%20classrooms%20and%20a%20seating%20capacity%20of%20around%201900.%20It%20has%20two%20auditoriums%20and%20students'%20hostel%20with%20a%20capacity%20of%20around%20550.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVisiting%20the%20excavated%20remains%20of%20Nalanda%20was%20exemplary.%20It%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20be%20at%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20seats%20of%20learning%20in%20the%20ancient%20world.%20This%20site%20offers%20a%20profound%20glimpse%20into%20the%20scholarly%20past%20that%20once%20thrived%20here.%20Nalanda%20has%20created%20an%20intellectual%20spirit%20that%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FUAKCZZqXn4%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FUAKCZZqXn4%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1803317488886616469%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20455-acre%20campus%20also%20has%20an%20international%20centre%2C%20an%20amphitheatre%2C%20a%20faculty%20club%2C%20and%20a%20sports%20complex.%20The%20Nalanda%20University%20campus%20is%20a%20'Net%20Zero'%20green%20campus.%20It%20runs%20on%20solar%20power%2C%20domestic%20and%20drinking%20water%20treatment%20plants%2C%20a%20water%20recycling%20plant%20and%20several%20water%20bodies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENalanda%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20is%20not%20just%20a%20name.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20an%20identity%2C%20it%20is%20respect.%20It%20is%20a%20value%2C%20a%20mantra%20and%20pride.%20It%20is%20a%20declaration%20that%20fire%20can%20consume%20books%2C%20but%20flames%20cannot%20erase%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20re-establishment%20of%20Nalanda%20University%20marks%20the%20golden%20age%20for%20India%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20new%20campus%20will%20be%20a%20symbol%20of%20India's%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nalanda%20University%20has%20been%20set%20up%20by%20an%20Act%20of%20Parliament%20in%202010.%20The%20law%20names%20it%20an%20institution%20of%20national%20importance.%20The%20President%20of%20India%20is%20the%20Visitor%20to%20the%20university.%20Renowned%20economist%20and%20Nobel%20laureate%20Amartya%20Sen%20had%20served%20as%20the%20first%20Chancellor%20of%20the%20university.%20Currently%2C%20Arvind%20Panagariya%2C%20also%20a%20well-known%20economist%2C%20is%20the%20university's%20Chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20to%20Rajgir%20comes%20shortly%20after%20he%20started%20his%20third%20consecutive%20term%20in%20the%20top%20post.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20JDU%20Nitish%20Kumar%2C%20whose%20critical%20support%20helped%20the%20BJP%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20gathering%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20congratulated%20the%20people%20of%20Bihar.%20%26quot%3BThis%20campus%20is%20an%20inspiration%20for%20Bihar%2C%20which%20is%20surging%20ahead%20on%20the%20path%20of%20development%20to%20reclaim%20its%20past%20glory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitically%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20showcase%20the%20development%20and%20inauguration%20of%20Nalanda%20University%20during%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20tenure%20as%20a%20key%20achievement.%20This%20is%20also%20significant%20because%20Bihar%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20next%20year.%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20JDU%20and%20BJP%20are%20allies%20in%20Bihar%2C%20but%20the%20equations%20have%20changed%20now%20that%20the%20BJP%20depends%20on%20JDU's%20support%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recently%20held%20general%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20JDU%20won%2012%20seats%20in%20Bihar%20each%20and%20ally%20Lok%20Janshakti%20(Ram%20Vilas)%20bagged%20five.%20The%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20won%20nine%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Nalanda%20inauguration%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20thanked%20neighbouring%20countries%20for%20their%20support%20in%20the%20university's%20development.%20%26quot%3BNalanda%20is%20not%20only%20the%20renaissance%20of%20India's%20heritage%20but%20also%20of%20the%20collective%20heritage%20of%20Asia%20and%20the%20world.%20The%20presence%20of%20representatives%20of%20so%20many%20nations%20for%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20university%20campus%20is%20unprecedented%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20welcoming%20the%20foreign%20dignitaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEducation%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20transcended%20borders%20and%20the%20binaries%20of%20profit%20and%20loss.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20education%20develops%2C%20economy%20and%20cultural%20roots%20are%20strengthened.%20If%20we%20look%20at%20developed%20countries%2C%20they%20became%20economic%20and%20cultural%20leaders%20after%20becoming%20leaders%20in%20education.%20Now%2C%20students%20and%20bright%20minds%20from%20across%20the%20world%20want%20to%20study%20in%20those%20countries.%20Once%2C%20this%20was%20the%20situation%20in%20our%20Nalanda%20and%20Vikramashila.%20It%20is%20not%20coincidence%20that%20when%20India%20was%20a%20leader%20in%20education%2C%20it%20was%20also%20on%20an%20economic%20high%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReiterating%20the%20goal%20to%20make%20India%20a%20developed%20country%20by%202047%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20revamping%20its%20education%20sector.%20My%20mission%20is%20to%20make%20India%20a%20global%20centre%20for%20education%2C%20to%20reclaim%20its%20identity%20as%20the%20world's%20most%20prominent%20knowledge%20centre.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718784960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F3hsv2ugg_nalanda-university_625x300_19_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-nalanda-university-nalanda-trip-within-10-days-of-3rd-terms-oath-good-omen-for-india-pm-modi-5922047%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20inaugurating%20Nalanda%20University's%20new%20campus%20in%20Bihar's%20Rajgir%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20today%20said%20his%20visit%20to%20Nalanda%20within%2010%20days%20of%20his%20third%20term%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20omen%26quot%3B%20in%20India's%20development%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-nalanda-university-nalanda-trip-within-10-days-of-3rd-terms-oath-good-omen-for-india-pm-modi-5922047%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-nalanda-university-nalanda-trip-within-10-days-of-3rd-terms-oath-good-omen-for-india-pm-modi-5922047%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-nalanda-university-nalanda-trip-within-10-days-of-3rd-terms-oath-good-omen-for-india-pm-modi-5922047%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Women%20are%20now%20writing%20for%20women%3A%20Lara%20Dutta%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718784718000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111107677%2Cimgsize-151230.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fwomen-are-now-writing-for-women-which-is-great-for-indian-cinema-and-ott-lara-dutta-exclusive%2Farticleshow%2F111107737.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg