%3EPolice%20believe%20Mr%20Swamy%20was%20beaten%20with%20sticks%20and%20then%20tied%20up%20and%20subject%20to%20electric%20shocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cops%20also%20believe%20Darshan%20-%20listed%20as%20Accused%20No%202%20-%20may%20have%20paid%20as%20much%20as%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20four%20men%20involved%20in%20the%20planning%20and%20execution%20of%20the%20gruesome%20crime%2C%20including%20arranging%20for%20Renuka%20Swamy%20to%20be%20brought%20from%20Chitradurga%20district%20to%20the%20state%20capital%2C%20a%20distance%20of%20200%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20the%20police%20believe%2C%20includes%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20paid%20to%20a%20man%20called%20Pradosh%20(alias%20Pawan)%20to%20handle%20all%20aspects%20of%20the%20abduction%20and%20murder%2C%20as%20well%20as%20disposal%20of%20the%20body.%20Two%20others%20-%20Nikhil%20and%20Keshavamurthy%20were%20given%20Rs%205%20lakh%20each%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20the%20murder%20and%20dumping%20the%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Factor-darshan-asked-3-men-to-take-blame-for-murder-paid-rs-15-lakh-probe-5880924%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EActor%20Darshan%20Asked%203%20To%20Take%20Blame%20For%20Murder%2C%20Paid%2015%20Lakh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20Rs%205%20lakh%20was%20to%20be%20paid%20to%20the%20families%20of%20two%20men%20-%20Raghavendra%20and%20Karthik%20-%20for%20submitting%20false%20confessions%20and%20going%20to%20prison%20in%20place%20of%20Darshan%2C%20Ms%20Pavithra%2C%20and%20the%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20Murder%20Of%20Renuka%20Swamy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Swamy%2C%20who%20worked%20for%20a%20pharmacy%20company%2C%20allegedly%20posted%20obscene%20messages%20on%20social%20media%20about%20Ms%20Gowda%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Mr%20Thogudeepa's%20co-star%20and%20close%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%2