p%3E2.%20With%20a%20few%20aging%20players%20in%20both%20the%20batting%20and%20bowling%20departments%2C%20how%20will%20you%20handle%20the%20transition%20phase%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20What%20are%20your%20views%20on%20split%20captaincy%2C%20fitness%20parameters%20concerning%20workload%20management%2C%20and%20addressing%20the%20team's%20failure%20to%20win%20ICC%20trophies%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir's%20name%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20the%20job%20even%20before%20he%20submitted%20the%20application.%20It%20was%20his%20skills%20leading%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20franchise%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20that%20made%20him%20the%20'ideal%20candidate'%20to%20fill%20Dravid's%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20recently%2C%20WV%20Raman%20had%20also%20wished%20Gambhir%20well%20for%20the%20role%2C%20saying%20he%20wishes%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%20winner%20well%20if%20he%20takes%20up%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20rated%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20captains%20in%20the%20IPL.%20He's%20always%20been%20intense%20and%20tactically%20sound.%20His%20success%20comes%20purely%20from%20his%20own%20efforts.%20He%20is%20committed%20to%20cricket%20and%20does%20not%20try%20to%20conform%20to%20others'%20expectations.%20If%20he%20takes%20up%20the%20India%20role%2C%20I%20wish%20him%20all%20the%20very%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Raman%20had%20told%20the%20portal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20has%20also%20put%20across%20his%20demands%20to%20the%20CAC%2C%20with%20the%20biggest%20arguably%20being%20two%20separate%20teams%20for%20white-ball%20and%20red-ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BCCI%20isn't%20expected%20to%20name%20the%20new%20head%20coach%20until%20the%20final%20stages%20of%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718784300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fb028fft_gautam-gambhir_640x480_03_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID