et%20Prediction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20never%20been%20a%20better%20time%20to%20be%20an%20Indian%2C%20and%20within%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20India%20will%20start%20adding%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20to%20its%20GDP%20every%2012%20to%2018%20months%2C%20putting%20us%20on%20track%20to%20be%20a%20%2430%20trillion%20economy%20by%202050%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20keynote%20at%20the%20Crisil%20Ratings'%20'Annual%20Infrastructure%20Summit'%2C%20Gautam%20Adani%20said%20it%20took%20India%2058%20years%20to%20get%20to%20its%20first%20trillion%20dollars%20of%20GDP%2C%2012%20years%20to%20get%20to%20the%20next%20trillion%20and%20just%20five%20years%20for%20the%20third%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGiven%20the%20pace%20at%20which%20India%20is%20growing%20and%20the%20way%20the%20government%20has%20been%20executing%20social%20and%20economic%20reforms%2C%20I%20anticipate%20that%20within%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20India%20will%20start%20adding%20a%20trillion%20dollars%20to%20its%20GDP%20every%2012%20to%2018%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Adani%20Group%20Chairman%20told%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20put%20us%20well%20on%20track%20to%20be%20a%20%2430%20trillion%20economy%20by%202050.%20At%20this%20time%2C%20I%20expect%20the%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%20to%20have%20exceeded%20%2440%20trillion.%20What%20this%20effectively%20means%20is%20that%20over%20the%20next%2026%20years%2C%20India%20will%20potentially%20add%20%2436%20trillion%20to%20its%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gautam%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%20capitalisation%20is%20over%20%245%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20other%20nation%20is%20remotely%20close%20to%20such%20a%20scale%20of%20possibility.%20There%20has%20never%20been%20a%20better%20time%20to%20be%20Indian%2C%26quot%