ncluded%20increasing%20the%20product%20range%2C%20organizing%20workshops%2C%20and%20promoting%20the%20brand.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20sadly%20been%20watching%20the%20craft%20become%20one%20of%20Hong%20Kong's%20disappearing%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitially%2C%20I%20hadn't%20thought%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhong-kong-food-stall-dai-pai-dong-family-business-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejoining%20the%20family%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20after%20I%20made%20the%20business%20plan%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223495%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Old%20grandfather%20holding%20young%20girl%20outside%20of%20Hong%20Kong%20shoe%20shop%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66725d82087acd2be9b4e3bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiru%20Wong%20with%20her%20grandfather%20Wong%20Tat-wing%20at%20the%20original%20Sindart%20shop.%3Cp%3EMiru%20Wong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20graduated%20at%2022%20with%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20and%20got%20started%20at%20the%20shop.%20Remaining%20true%20to%20her%20grandfather's%20vision%20of%20providing%20affordable%20options%2C%20Wong%20has%20kept%20prices%20reasonable.%20The%20cheapest%20pair%20is%20made%20without%20embroidery%20and%20costs%2099%20Hong%20Kong%20dollars%2C%20or%20%2412.%20For%20more%20detailed%20shoes%2C%20prices%20go%20up%20to%20around%20HK%24300%2C%20or%20%2438.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWong%20says%20most%20of%20the%20materials%20%E2%80%94%20including%20nylon%2C%20silk%2C%20satin%2C%20and%20brocade%20%E2%80%94%20are%20sourced%20from%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20Europe.%20She%20says%20the%20store%20sells%2080%20to%20100%20pairs%20of%20shoes%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20the%20shop's%20third-generation%20owner%2C%20Wong%2C%20now%2033%2C%20has%20had%20to%20make%20changes.%