7%20trillion%20as%20its%20shares%20slipped%20nearly%20half%20a%20per%20cent.%20Apple%20was%20valued%20at%20%243.286%20trillion%20as%20its%20share%20fell%201%25%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENvidia%20shares%20have%20risen%20nearly%20three-fold%20this%20year%20so%20far%20against%20a%2019%25%20rise%20in%20Microsoft%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENvidia%20Corp%20went%20public%20in%201999%20at%20a%20price%20of%20%2412%20per%20share.%20Nvidia%20shares%20have%20skyrocketed%20multiple%20times%20since%20its%20listing%20driven%20by%20the%20development%20of%20gaming%20and%20new-age%20technology%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20in%20Nvidia%20IPO%20in%201999%20would%20have%20given%20astronomical%20returns%2C%20making%20you%20a%20millionaire.%20How%3F%20Let's%20show%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20rupee-dollar%20exchange%20rate%20of%20around%2043%20in%201999%2C%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20would%20have%20earned%20around%2019%20shares.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20Nvidia%20Corp%20has%20announced%20stock%20splits%20to%20reward%20its%20investors%20and%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20investors%20to%20own%20its%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECumulatively%2C%20one%20share%20of%20Nvidia%20bought%20prior%20to%20stock%20splits%20in%202000%20has%20turned%20into%20480%20Nvidia%20shares%20as%20of%20today.%20It%20means%2019%20shares%20bought%20in%20the%20IPO%20would%20have%20turned%20into%209%2C120%20shares%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20current%20trading%20price%20of%20%24135%20per%20share%2C%20these%20shares%20are%20valued%20at%20%241.231%20million%20(around%20Rs%2010.3%20crore%20at%20the%20current%20exchange%20rate%20of%2083.40).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2010%2C000%20would%20have%20made%20an%20investor%20a%20crorepati%20in%20around%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718778360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbac0a