ky.com%2Fstory%2Fmicroplastics-found-in-penises-for-first-time-researchers-say-raising-questions-over-impact-on-sexual-health-13155260%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmicroplastics-found-in-penises-for-first-time-researchers-say-raising-questions-over-impact-on-sexual-health-13155260%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmicroplastics-found-in-penises-for-first-time-researchers-say-raising-questions-over-impact-on-sexual-health-13155260%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Sensorineural%20Deafness%2C%20Hearing%20Loss%20Alka%20Yagnik%20Is%20Diagnosed%20With%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENational%20Award-winning%20singer%20Alka%20Yagnik%20is%20battling%20with%20sensorineural%20deafness%2C%20a%20condition%20in%20which%20a%20person%20may%20struggle%20to%20hear%20faint%20sounds%2C%20understand%20speech%20clearly%20or%20differentiate%20between%20different%20sounds.%C2%A0In%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8U2sbzsa2Q%2F%3Fhl%3Den%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%2058-year-old%20recounted%20the%20alarming%20moment%20she%20lost%20her%20hearing%20after%20a%20routine%20flight.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20walked%20out%20of%20a%20flight%2C%20I%20suddenly%20felt%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20hear%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20singer%20wrote.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Yagnik%20warned%20her%20%E2%80%9Cfans%20and%20young%20colleagues%E2%80%9D%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20exposure%20to%20very%20loud%20music%20and%20prolonged%20use%20of%20headphones.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20sensorineural%20deafness%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSensorineural%20deafness%2C%20also%20known%20as%20sensorineural%20hearing%20loss%20(SNHL)%2C%20occurs%20when%20there%20is%20damage%20to%20the%20inner%20ear%20or%20the%20nerve%20pathways%20from%20the%20ear%20to%20the%20brain%2C%20according%20to%20Healthline.%C2%A0The%20condition%20is%20usually%20permanent.%20Treatments%20like%20hearing%20aids%20or%20cochlear%20implants%20can%20help%20manage%20it%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20severe%20the%20condition%20is.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ECauses%20of%20sensorineural%20deafness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAgeing%3A%20As%20people%20get%20older%2C%20the%20parts%20of%20the%20inner%20ear%20can%20wear%20out%2C%20leading%20to%20gradual%20hearing%20loss%20over%20time.%20About%20one-third%20of%20people%20between%2065%20and%2074%20years%20old%20have%20some%20trouble%20hearing.%20By%20age%2075%2C%20about%20half%20of%20people%20have%20hearing%20problems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENoise%20exposure%3A%20Being%20exposed%20to%20loud%20noises%2C%20like%20gunfire%20or%20concerts%20with%20loud%20machinery%2C%20can%20hurt%20the%20tiny%20hair%20cells%20in%20your%20ear%20or%20the%20nerve%20that%20carries%20sound%20to%20your%20brain.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20SNHL.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGenetic%20factors%3A%20Some%20people%20are%20born%20with%20SNHL%20because%20of%20genes%20they%20inherit%20or%20infections%20their%20mothers%20had%20during%20pregnancy%2C%20like%20rubella%20or%20cytomegalovirus.%20Problems%20during%20birth%2C%20like%20not%20getting%20enough%20oxygen%2C%20can%20also%20cause%20SNHL.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIllnesses%20and%20infections%3A%20Some%20sicknesses%20caused%20by%20viruses%20or%20bacteria%2C%20like%20measles%20or%20meningitis%2C%20can%20damage%20your%20inner%20ear%20and%20cause%20hearing%20loss.%20Autoimmune%20disorders%2C%20where%20your%20body's%20defences%20attack%20itself%2C%20can%20also%20hurt%20your%20hearing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMedications%3A%20Certain%20medicines%2C%20especially%20ones%20used%20for%20cancer%20treatment%20or%20strong%20infections%2C%20can%20have%20side%20effects%20that%20hurt%20the%20parts%20of%20your%20ear%20that%20help%20you%20hear.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHead%20Trauma%3A%20Physical%20trauma%20to%20the%20head%20or%20skull%20fractures%20can%20damage%20the%20auditory%20nerve%20or%20the%20inner%20ear%2C%20causing%20SNHL.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718776860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F21gveemg_alka-yagnik_625x300_18_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-causes-sensorineural-deafness-the-hearing-loss-alka-yagnik-is-battling-5921569%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22National%20Award-winning%20singer%20Alka%20Yagnik%20is%20battling%20with%20sensorineural%20deafness%2C%20a%20condition%20in%20which%20a%20person%20may%20struggle%20to%20hear%20faint%20sounds%2C%20understand%20speech%20clearly%20or%20differentiate%20between%20different%20sounds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-causes-sensorineural-deafness-the-hearing-loss-alka-yagnik-is-battling-5921569%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-causes-sensorineural-deafness-the-hearing-loss-alka-yagnik-is-battling-5921569%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhat-causes-sensorineural-deafness-the-hearing-loss-alka-yagnik-is-battling-5921569%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi%20Visits%20Ruins%20Of%20Ancient%20Nalanda%20University%20In%20Bihar's%20Rajgir%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visited%20the%20ruins%20of%20ancient%20Nalanda%2C%20a%20UNESCO%20world%20heritage%20site%2C%20in%20Rajgir%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruins%20of%20ancient%20Nalanda%20comprise%20the%20archaeological%20remains%20of%20a%20monastic%20and%20scholastic%20institution.%20It%20includes%20stupas%2C%20shrines%2C%20viharas%20(residential%20and%20educational%20buildings)%20and%20important%20artworks%20in%20stucco%2C%20stone%20and%20metal.%20Nalanda%20stands%20out%20as%20the%20most%20ancient%20university%20of%20