0lives%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20heinous%20terror-related%20air%20disasters%20in%20the%20history%20of%20civil%20aviation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Consulate%20General%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E23%20June%202024%20marks%20the%2039th%20Anniversary%20of%20the%20cowardly%20terrorist%20bombing%20of%20Air%20India%20flight%20182%20(Kanishka)%2C%20in%20which%20329%20innocent%20victims%2C%20including%2086%20children%2C%20lost%20their%20lives%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20heinous%20terror-related%20air%20disasters%20in%20the%20history%20of%20civil%20aviation.%20(2%2F3)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20India%20in%20Vancouver%20(%40cgivancouver)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcgivancouver%2Fstatus%2F1803191567437427088%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Memorial%20Service%20is%20scheduled%20at%201830%20hrs%20on%20June%2023%2C%202024%20at%20the%20Air%20India%20Memorial%20at%20Stanley%20Park's%20Ceperley%20Playground%20area.%C2%A0%40cgivancouver%20encourages%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20Diaspora%20to%20join%20the%20event%20in%20a%20show%20of%20solidarity%20against%20terrorism.%20%40HCI_Ottawa%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20India%20Flight%20travelling%20from%20Montreal%20to%20London%20had%20blown%20up%2031%2C000%20feet%20above%20the%20ground%20when%20a%20bomb%20planted%20by%20Canadian%20Sikh%20terrorists%20went%20off.%20The%20329%20passengers%20killed%20in%20the%20incident%20included%20268%20Canadian%20citizens%2C%2027%20British%20citizens%2C%20and%2024%20Indian%20citizens.%20This%20bombing%20is%20among%20the%20deadliest%20acts%20of%20aviation%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECanada's%20Parliament%20marked%20the%20one-year%20anniversary%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20by%20holding%20a%20moment%20of%20silence%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20on%20Tuesday%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn(Video%20Source%20-%20Canadian%20Parliament%20Official%20Website)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSGkovpiWXc%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSGkovpiWXc%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20IANS%20(%40ians_india)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fians_india%2Fstatus%2F1803269964805161067%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2019%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Consulate%20General's%20post%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Parliament%20observing%20a%20moment%20of%20silence%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20Nijjar%2C%20who%20was%20shot%20dead%20outside%20a%20gurdwara%20in%20British%20Columbia%20last%20year.%20The%20Justin%20Trudeau-led%20Canadian%20administration%20has%20alleged%20that%20Indian%20government%20agents%20could%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20killing.%20New%20Delhi%20has%20trashed%20the%20allegations%2C%20describing%20them%20as%20motivated%20and%20absurd.%20Bilateral%20ties%20have%20since%20nosedived.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENijjar's%20murder%20is%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20and%20four%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20released%20by%20news%20agency%20IANS%20shows%20members%20of%20the%20Canadian%20parliament%20observing%20silence%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Commons.%20Speaker%20Greg%20Fergus%20starts%20the%20memorial%20by%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BFollowing%20discussions%20among%20representatives%20of%20all%20parties%20in%20the%20House%2C%20I%20understand%20there%20is%20an%20agreement%20to%20observe%20a%20moment%20of%20silence%20in%20memory%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20assassinated%20in%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20one%20year%20ago%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20days%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20a