0outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20The%20Information%20the%20suggestion%20that%20AWS%20was%20concerned%20about%20upsetting%20Nvidia%20was%20%26quot%3Bspeculative%20and%20incorrect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said%20Amazon%20worked%20closely%20with%20Nvidia%20to%20develop%20features%20in%20the%20DGX%20Cloud%20offering%20that%20offered%20customers%20%26quot%3Bthe%20best%20of%20both%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20deep%20collaboration%20with%20Nvidia%20that%20goes%20back%20more%20than%2013%20years%2C%20when%20together%20we%20launched%20the%20world's%20first%20GPU%20cloud%20instance%20on%20AWS%2C%20and%20today%20we%20offer%20the%20widest%20range%20of%20Nvidia%20GPU%20solutions%20for%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon's%20spokesperson%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20DGX%20Cloud%2C%20Nvidia%20has%20creatively%20maneuvered%20itself%20into%20a%20position%20where%20its%20own%20customers%20are%20helping%20it%20compete%20with%20them.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-leadership-style-insiders-tough-boss-admit-mistakes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E's%20aggressive%20strategy%20to%20maintain%20dominance%20doesn't%20stop%20there%2C%20per%20The%20Information.%C2%A0Nvidia%20is%20also%20requiring%20customers%20to%20build%20out%20more%20space%20to%20house%20the%20GPUs%20they%20buy%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20and%20telling%20them%20how%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%20will%20not%20ship%20GPUs%20unless%20the%20customer%20can%20certify%20that%20they%20have%20data%20center%20capacity%20in%20which%20to%20place%20those%20GPUs%2C%26quot%3B%20Raul%20Martynek%2C%20who%20works%20with%20cloud%20providers%20as%20the%20CEO%20of%20DataBank%2C%20told%20The%20Information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20titan%20chipmaker%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20demanding%20its%20clients%20