%2C%26quot%3B%20Giants%20chairman%20Greg%20Johnson%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mlb.com%2Fpress-release%2Fpress-release-san-francisco-and-the-baseball-community-mourns-the-loss-of-san-francisco-giants-legend-and-hall-of-famer-willie-mays%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CToday%2520we%2520have%2520lost%2520a%2Cis%2520the%2520ultimate%2520Forever%2520Giant.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWillie%20Mays%2C%20the%20Hall%20of%20Famer%20with%20a%20career%20that%20spanned%2022%20seasons%2C%20has%20died%20at%20age%2093%2C%20the%20San%20Francisco%20Giants%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSFGiants%2Fstatus%2F1803229363770478912%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20have%20lost%20a%20true%20legend%2C%26quot%3B%20Giants%20chairman%20Greg%20Johnson%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mlb.com%2Fpress-release%2Fpress-release-san-francisco-and-the-baseball-community-mourns-the-loss-of-san-francisco-giants-legend-and-hall-of-famer-willie-mays%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CToday%2520we%2520have%2520lost%2520a%2Cis%2520the%2520ultimate%2520Forever%2520Giant.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20pantheon%20of%20baseball%20greats%2C%20Willie%20Mays'%20combination%20of%20tremendous%20talent%2C%20keen%20intellect%2C%20showmanship%2C%20and%20boundless%20joy%20set%20him%20apart.%20A%2024-time%20All-Star%2C%20the%20Say%20Hey%20Kid%20is%20the%20ultimate%20Forever%20Giant.%20He%20had%20a%20profound%20influence%20not%20only%20on%20the%20game%20of%20baseball%2C%20but%20on%20the%20fabric%20of%20America.%20He%20was%20an%20inspiration%20and%20a%20hero%20who%20will%20be%20forever%20remembered%20and%20deeply%20missed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20his%20death%2C%20May%20had%20been%20the%20oldest%20living%20member%20of%20the%20Baseball%20Hall%20of%20Fame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicknamed%20the%20%26quot%3BSay%20Hey%20Kid%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20way%20he%20greeted%20people%2C%20Mays%20joined%20the%20Birmingham%20Black%20Barons%20of%20the%20Negro%20American%20League%20in%201948%20at%20age%2016%2C%20per%20the%20MLB.%20In%201951%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20New%20York%20Giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20arrived%20in%20New%20York%20City%20on%20a%20Friday%20at%204%20o'clock%2C%26quot%3B%20Mays%20said%20during%20his%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20induction%20ceremony%20in%201979%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fwillie-mays-baseball-great-dies-age-93%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BScared%20to%20death%20with%20three%20bats%20in%20my%20little%20briefcase%2C%20my%20glove%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20uniform%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20hat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20his%20first%20season%2C%20he%20was%20named%20the%20National%20League%20Rookie%20of%20the%20Year%2C%20per%20the%20MLB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMays%20would%20go%20on%20to%20play%2021%20seasons%20with%20the%20Giants%20before%20being%20traded%20to%20the%20New%20York%20Mets%20for%20the%201972-73%20season%2C%20which%20would%20be%20his%20last.%20He%20finished%20his%20career%20with%203%2C293%20hits%20and%20660%20home%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMays%20was%20named%20the%20league's%20Most%20Valuable%20Player%20twice%20and%20won%20the%20World%20Series%20with%20the%20Giants%20in%201954.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20retired%20in%201973%20with%2024%20All-Star%20awards%20and%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20Baseball%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20in%201979.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Giants%20retired%20his%20No.%2024%20jersey%20on%20May%2012%2C%201972%2C%20and%20the%20Mets%20did%20the%20same%2050%20years%20later%20on%20August%2027%2C%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMays%20married%20Margherite%20Wendell%20Chapman%20in%201956%2C%20and%20they%20adopted%20a%20son%2C%20Michael%2C%20together%20before%20divorcing%20in%201963.%20In%201971%2C%20he%20married%20Mae%20Louise%20Allen%2C%20who%20died%20from%20Alzheimer's%20disease%20in%202013%20at%20the%20age%20of%2074%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mlb.com%2Fnews%2Fwillie-mays-giants-announce-death-of-mae-louise-allen-mays%2Fc-45240424%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMLB%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMays%20died%20the%20day%20after%20he%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sfchronicle.com%2Fsports%2Fgiants%2Farticle%2Fwillie-mays-rickwood-game-19504800.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco%20Chronicle%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20attend%20the%20Negro%20Leagues%20tribute%20game%20between%20the%20Giants%20and%20St.%20Louis%20Cardinals%20in%20Birmingham%2C%20Alabama%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20June%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20father%20has%20passed%20away%20peacefully%20and%20among%20loved%20ones%2C%26quot%3B%20Michael%20Mays%20told%20the%20Chronicle%20on%20Tuesday.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20you%20all%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20my%20broken%20heart%20for%20the%20unwavering%20love%20you%20have%20shown%20him%20over%20the%20years.%20You%20have%20been%20his%20life's%20blood.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhall-of-famer-willie-mays-has-died-at-93-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718761406000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667236afa76074d191cd3439%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhall-of-famer-willie-mays-has-died-at-93-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Willie%20Mays%2C%20who%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20Baseball%20Hall%20of%20Fame%20in%201979%2C%20has%20died%20at%20age%2093.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A113%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2