%2C%20ethics%2C%20and%20standards%20we%20all%20believe%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20owner's%20email%20comes%20as%20Lewis%20faces%20criticism%20related%20to%20the%20phone-hacking%20scandal%20that%20rocked%20the%20UK%20starting%20in%202011%20when%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20reporters%20at%20a%20British%20tabloid%20had%20hacked%20the%20phone%20records%20of%20celebrities%20and%20private%20citizens%20and%20that%20some%20had%20paid%20sources%20for%20information.%20Lewis%20was%20brought%20into%20News%20Corp.%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20fallout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F06%2F15%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fwill-lewis-records-uk-editor.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%20reported%20that%20Lewis%20himself%20had%20assigned%20stories%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bfraudulently%20obtained%26quot%3B%20phone%20and%20company%20records%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20when%20he%20was%20a%20business%20editor%20at%20The%20Sunday%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Finvestigations%2F2024%2F06%2F16%2Fwashington-post-editor-robert-winnett%2F%3Fpwapi_token%3DeyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..DDD4jH-fy-kVcuOwQgpkRM0T-cO17vfxEMsful9ttEw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPost%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20a%20story%20on%20Sunday%20that%20said%20a%20self-described%20%26quot%3Bthief%26quot%3B%20who%20stole%20records%20for%20stories%20was%20connected%20to%20Lewis%20and%20Robert%20Winnett%2C%20the%20Post's%20incoming%20editor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-work-life-balance-debilitating-phrase-career-circle-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBezos%3C%2Fa%3E%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20BI.%20The%20Post%20did%20not%20provide%20comment%20when%20reached%20by%20BI.%20Previously%2C%20The%20Post%20told%20The%20Tim