0wingmen.%20Yet%20recent%20remarks%20from%20Air%20Force%20officials%20suggest%20those%20wingmen%20have%20a%20more%20certain%20place%20within%20America's%20future%20airpower%20apparatus%20than%20the%20NGAD%20fighter%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20directly%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20NGAD%20program%2C%20which%20was%20supposed%20to%20have%20a%20contract%20announced%20this%20year%2C%20Air%20Force%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Gen.%20David%20Allvin%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20the%206th%20generation%20fighter's%20future%20may%20be%20far%20from%20certain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20deliberations%20are%20still%20underway%2C%20there's%20been%20no%20decision%20made.%20We're%20looking%20at%20a%20lot%20of%20very%20difficult%20options%20that%20we%20have%20to%20consider%2C%26quot%3B%20Allvin%20told%20reporters%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20could%20mark%20an%20even%20more%20dramatic%20shift%20away%20from%20the%20status%20quo%2C%20Air%20Force%20officials%20have%20also%20hinted%20at%20a%20potential%20return%20to%20a%20fighter%20development%20model%20proposed%20by%20Air%20Force%20Acquisition%20Chief%20Will%20Roper%20back%20in%202019%2C%20in%20which%20smaller%20batches%20of%20fighters%20would%20be%20designed%20to%20operate%20with%20shorter%20lifespans%2C%20allowing%20for%20rapid%20design%20and%20technology%20changes%20as%20the%20threat%20landscape%20evolves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20concept%20was%20dubbed%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Fair-force-creates-new-peo-for-ngad-applying-digital-century-series-idea%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edigital%20century%20series%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20approach%20at%20the%20time%2C%20thanks%20to%20its%20emphasis%20on%20modern%20all-digital%20aircraft%20design%20and%20its%20similarities%20to%20the%20rapidly%20changing%20fighter%20designs%20of%20the%201950s%20and%20'60s%20%E2%80%94%20ranging%20from%20the%20North%20American%20F-100%20Super%20Sabre%20to%20the%20Convair%20F-106%20Delta%20Dart.%20Most%20modern%20fighter%20designs%2C%20like%20Lockheed%20Martin's%20F-35%2C%20for%20example%2C%20are%20meant%20to%20fly%20for%20a%20half-century%20or%20more%2C%20with%20long%20service%20lives%20seen%20as%20justification%20for%20their%20massive%20developmental%20budgets.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20F-35's%20model%20comes%20with%20at%20least%20two%20significant%20drawbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20F-35B%20Lightning%20II%20aircraft%20from%20the%20F-35%20Integrated%20Test%20Force%20(ITF)%20successfully%20landed%20onboard%20HMS%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20on%201%20November%202018%20marking%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Development%20Testing%20(DT-2)%20of%20first-of-class%20flying%20trials%20(FOCFT).%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664f9e5fa961b37edf397a61%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20F-35B%20Lightning%20II%20aircraft%20from%20the%20F-35%20Integrated%20Test%20Force%20(ITF)%20successfully%20landed%20onboard%20HMS%20Queen%20Elizabeth%2C%20marking%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Development%20Testing%20(DT-2)%20of%20first-of-class%20flying%20trials%20(FOCFT).%3Cp%3ERELEASED%20%2F%20U.S.%20Navy%20Photograph%20by%20Liz%20Wolter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20technological%2C%20as%20purchasing%20a%20new%20fighter%20today%20that%20can%20remain%20dominant%20into%20the%202070s%20is%20all%20but%20impossible%20without%20adapting%20to%20or%20adopting%20a%20variety%20of%20new%20technologies%20along%20the%20way.%20Being%20married%20to%20a%20single%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20design%20until%20what%20could%20conceivably%20fly%20until%20the%20close%20of%20this%20century%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20rapidly%20adjust%20to%20counter%20new%20threats%20as%20they%20emerge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20pursue%20a%20lot%20of%20eggs%20in%20one%20basket%20and%20then%20find%20that%20the%20threat%20has%20advanced%2C%26quot%3B%20Allvin%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20drawback%20is%20economic%2C%20with%20lifespan%20sustainment%20representing%20a%20huge%20portion%20of%20a%20fighter%20program's%20overall%20cost.%20To%20use%20the%20F-35%20as%20an%20example%20again%2C%20its%20overall%20program%20cost%20is%20now%20estimated%20to%20exceed%20%242%20trillion%20over%20the%20jet's%20lifetime%2C%20but%20some%20%241.6%20trillion%20of%20that%20%E2%80%94%20a%20whopping%2080%25%20of%20the%20total%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20comes%20from%20maintenance%20and%20sustainment%20over%20its%20decadeslong%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoper's%20Digital%20Century%20Series%20model%20aimed%20to%20curtail%20these%20costs%20by%20instead%20leaning%20into%20agile%20software%20development%2C%20digital%20engineering%2C%20and%20open-system%20modular%20architecture%20to%20allow%20the%20Air%20Force%20and%20its%20prime%20contractors%20to%20rapidly%20develop%20and%20field%20new%20fighter%20designs%20with%20enough%20regularity%20to%20limit%20the%20lifespan%20of%20each%20to%20just%20a%20decade%20or%20two.%20This%20would%20allow%20the%20Air%20Force%20to%20continuously%20field%20the%20most%20advanced%20airpower%20assets%20on%20the%20planet%20while%20also%20eliminating%20the%20most%20expensive%20(later)%20years%20of%20the%20sustainment%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Built%20to%20last'%20is%20a%20tremendous%2020th-century%20bumper%20sticker%2C%20and%20the%20assumption%20then%20was%2C%20whatever%20you%20had%20was%20relevant%20as%20long%20as%20it%20lasts%2C%26quot%3B%20Allvin%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20that's%20true%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20indeed%20several%20good%20reasons%20to%20transition%20to%20a%20model%20that%20could%20produce%20a%20new%20fighter%20design%20every%20decade%20or%20two.%20Not%20only%20would%20such%20a%20model%20mean%20cutting%20out%20the%20most%20expensive%20decades%20of%20a%20fighter's%20lifespan%2C%20but%20it%20would%20also%20allow%20for%20the%20rapid%20adoption%20of%20emerging%20technologies%20in%20the%20steady%20flow%20of%20new%20fighters%20maturing%20toward%20service.%20That%20steady%20flow%20of%20new%20designs%20could%20be%20a%20boon%20unto%20itself%2C%20as%20it%20could%20potentially%20make%20fighter%20designs%20a%20truly%20competitive%20industry%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20there%20are%20really%20only%20three%20American%20firms%20left%20in%20the%20fighter%20business%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20trade%20largely%20on%20other%20types%20of%20military%20and%20commercial%20technologies%20across%20their%20portfolio%2C%20as%20fighter%20contracts%20have%20been%20few%20and%20far%20between%20in%20the%20modern%20era.%20With%20Lockheed%20Martin's%20Skunk%20Works%20winning%20both%201991's%20Advanced%20Tactical%20Fighter%20competition%20and%202001's%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%20Competition%2C%20it's%20been%2049%20years%20since%20any%20company%20other%20than%20Lockheed%20Martin%20has%20won%20the%20right%20to%20field%20a%20new%20clean-sheet%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lockheed%20martin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b3ba28ad7751421008b4858%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221085%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Lockheed%20Martin%20logo%20is%20displayed%20near%20a%20company-made%20drone%20during%20an%20exhibit.%3Cp%3EIsaac%20Brekken%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Digital%20Century%20Series%20model%20would%20see%20new%20fighter%20designs%20being%20fielded%20every%20five%20to%2010%20years%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20the%20development%20cycle%20for%20the%20next%20new%20fighter%20would%20likely%20begin%20almost%20immediately%20after%20a%20contract%20is%20awarded%20for%20the%20current%20one.%20This%20could%20create%20the%20necessary%20incentive%20for%20a%20wider%20variety%20of%20firms%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20fighter%20design%20space%2C%20and%20that%20competition%20could%20be%20made%20even%20greater%20by%20separating%20design%20and%20production%20contracts%20into%20separate%20awards.%20This%20could%20allow%20newer%20or%20smaller%20firms%20that%20lack%20the%20production%20infrastructure%20required%20to%20mass%20produce%20new%20stealth%20fighters%20to%20compete%20in%20the%20design%20space%2C%20with%20production%20contracts%20potentially%20still%20awarded%20to%20long-standing%20primes%20like%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20Boeing%2C%20or%20Northrop%20Grumman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20there%20are%20also%20some%20glaring%20issues%20with%20the%20Air%20Force%20potentially%20reverting%20to%20Roper's%20concept%20for%20fighter%20production%20this%20late%20in%20the%20game%20for%20NGAD%2C%20which%20has%20been%20in%20active%20development%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20already%20built%20and%20flown%20a%20full-scale%20flight%20demonstrator%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20and%20we%20broke%20records%20in%20doing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Roper%20told%20Defense%20News%20at%20the%20Air%20Force%20Association's%20Air%2C%20Space%20and%20Cyber%20Conference%20in%202020.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20ready%20to%20go%20and%20build%20the%20next-generation%20aircraft%20in%20a%20way%20that%20has%20never%20happened%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20aircraft%20designs%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fthe-race-to-field-the-most-advanced-stealth-fighter-engines-in-the-world%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epowerful%20and%20efficient%20engines%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20developed%20to%20power%20them%2C%20have%20continued%20to%20mature%20since%2C%20with%20Northrop%20Grumman%20bowing%20out%20of%20the%20competition%20in%20early%202024%20and%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20Boeing%20seemingly%20competing%20for%20the%20contract%20award.%20This%20could%20spell%20a%20significant%20cost%20problem%3A%20With%20this%20effort%20maturing%20for%20about%20a%20decade%20now%2C%20transitioning%20away%20from%20a%20traditional%20fighter%20acquisition%20model%20at%20this%20stage%20would%20force%20a%20revision%20of%20the%20designs%20in%20testing%20to%20embrace%20lower%20costs%20and%20shorter%20operational%20lifespans%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20why%20Air%20Force%20Secretary%20Frank%20Kendall%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.airandspaceforces.com%2Fkendall-air-force-ngad-design%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edescribed%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20a%20change%20as%20%26quot%3Bfar%20too%20expensive%26quot%3B%20in%202022%20when%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20Digital%20Century%20Series%20lost%20favor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Air%20Force%20Secretary%20Frank%20Kendall%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66166d5816bde8d4ead73e43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAir%20Force%20Secretary%20Frank%20Kendall.%3Cp%3ETom%20Williams%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20now%20appears%20to%20be%20coming%20around%20to%20Roper's%20way%20of%20thinking%20but%20now%20must%20weigh%20the%20costs%20of%20changing%20the%20requirements%20of%20a%20program%20that's%20already%20seen%20well%20over%20a%20billion%20dollars%20and%20several%20years'%20worth%20of%20investment.%20The%20stakes%20of%20these%20deliberations%20are%20already%20high%2C%20but%20they're%20made%20even%20higher%20because%20of%20the%20tight%20timetable%20created%20by%20what%20some%20might%20call%20short-sighted%20decision-making%20around%20the%20branch's%20last%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20program%2C%20the%20F-22%20Raptor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20first%20taking%20flight%20in%201997%2C%20the%20F-22%20Raptor%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fwhy-america-never-sold-the-f-22-raptor-to-foreign-countries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estill%20broadly%20considered%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20the%20most%20capable%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20on%20the%20planet%20thanks%20to%20an%20awe-inspiring%20combination%20of%20stealth%2C%20sensor%20fusion%2C%20and%20good%20old-fashioned%20power.%20But%2C%20because%20the%20F-22%20entered%20service%20after%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20and%20well%20before%20Xi%20Jinping's%20rise%20to%20power%2C%20its%20production%20run%20was%20cut%20short%20after%20just%20186%20airframes%20were%20produced%2C%20only%20around%20150%20of%20which%20were%20combat%20coded%20(or%20equipped%20with%20all%20the%20necessary%20systems%20for%20combat).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20much%20of%20its%20production%20infrastructure%20then%20cannibalized%20by%20the%20F-35%20program%2C%20it%20became%20all%20but%20impossible%20to%20produce%20more%20Raptors.%20With%20each%20F-22%20airframe%20rated%20for%20around%206%2C000%20flight%20hours%2C%20these%20aircraft%20can%20undergo%20expensive%20service-life%20extension%20programs%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20they%20will%20simply%20wear%20out.%20And%20without%20a%20new%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20in%20production%20to%20replace%20them%2C%20the%20US%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20leaving%20the%20air%20superiority%20mission%20gapped%20for%20some%20time%20as%20the%20new%20Digital%20Century%20Series%20fighters%20take%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22F-22%20raptor%20f%2022%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5de95eb6e94e865d9a0afe5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222001%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EUSAF%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Allvin's%20comments%20may%20have%20come%20with%20something%20of%20an%20ulterior%20motive.%20With%20competition%20for%20the%20NGAD%20contract%20underway%20and%20the%20Air%20Force%20clearly%20recognizing%20how%20the%20future%20of%20fighter%20acquisitions%20may%20be%20in%20flux%2C%20these%20statements%20may%20be%20a%20means%20of%20placing%20public%20pressure%20on%20Lockheed%20and%20Boeing%20to%20revise%20their%20proposals%2C%20particularly%20in%20terms%20of%20cost.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20may%20intend%20to%20transition%20toward%20the%20Digital%20Century%20Series%20acquisition%20model%20moving%20forward%20but%20may%20be%20using%20the%20public%20groundwork%20for%20that%20transition%20to%20create%20negotiating%20leverage%20with%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20Boeing%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20possible%20that%20the%20Air%20Force%20has%20made%20these%20announcements%20to%20sound%20the%20alarm%20among%20the%20lawmaker%20class%2C%20which%20could%20potentially%20bolster%20the%20branch's%20buying%20power%20in%20the%202026%20National%20Defense%20Authorization%20Act%20to%20ensure%20NGAD%20continues%20unfettered%20despite%20the%20Air%20Force's%20pressing%20need%20to%20also%20fund%20the%20production%20of%20new%20B-21%20Raider%20stealth%20bombers%20and%20the%20already%20well-over-budget%20Sentinel%20ICBM%20meant%20to%20replace%20America's%20aging%20Minuteman%20III%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20either%20of%20the%20above%20two%20possibilities%20is%20the%20case%20won't%20likely%20be%20clear%20until%20well%20after%20the%20NGAD%20contract%20%E2%80%94%20in%20whatever%20form%20it%20may%20ultimately%20manifest%20%E2%80%94%20has%20been%20awarded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20future%20of%20the%20NGAD%20fighter%20itself%20may%20now%20be%20in%20question%2C%20the%20AI-enabled%20drones%20meant%20to%20fly%20alongside%20it%2C%20being%20developed%20within%20the%20Collaborative%20Combat%20Aircraft%20(CCA)%20program%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20progressing%20at%20full%20steam%20ahead%2C%20with%20Allvin%20pointing%20to%20similar%2010-year%20acquisition%20timelines%20for%20new%20CCA%20drones%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20similarly%20allow%20the%20branch%20to%20rapidly%20field%20new%20technologies%20and%20capabilities%20as%20they%20emerge%20while%20keeping%20costs%20relatively%20low%20for%20each%20iteration%20of%20these%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20with%20modular%20systems%20shared%20across%20platforms%20to%20keep%20prices%20down.%20These%20drones%20are%20already%20expected%20to%20fly%20alongside%20the%20forthcoming%20Block%204%20F-35%20and%20could%20certainly%20end%20up%20accompanying%20other%20modernized-but-older%20jets%20like%20the%20F-22%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fcongress-to-the-air-force-buy-more-f-15ex-eagle-iis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EF-15EX%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20bit%20further%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20question%2C%20however%2C%20will%20soon%20become%20whether%20it%20makes%20more%20sense%20to%20extend%20the%20lifespan%20of%20the%20F-22%20long%20enough%20to%20compensate%20for%20delays%20in%20fielding%20its%20replacement%20or%20fielding%20a%20new%20high-end%20fighter%20that%20might%20not%20have%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20remain%20competitive%20into%20the%202070s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%20of%20which%20path%20the%20Air%20Force%20ultimately%20chooses%2C%20that%20choice%20will%20only%20get%20pricier%20the%20longer%20the%20branch%20waits%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220968b33e-9868-4c09-9135-012b741569f6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20MORE%20FROM%20SANDBOXX%20NEWS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fis-the-pacific-better-than-band-of-brothers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EIs%20%26quot%3BThe%20Pacific%26quot%3B%20better%20than%20%26quot%3BBand%20of%20Brothers%26quot%3B%3F%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fdelta-forces-approach-to-medical-training%2F%5C%22%20targ