onsumer%20(D2C)%20brand%20Aamor%C3%A9%20(Italian%20word%20for%20love)%2C%20to%20make%20people%20abroad%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20authentic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fmost-expensive-mangoes-in-india-alphonso-miyazaki-noorjahan-kohitur-sindhri%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphonso%20mangoes%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwned%20by%20smallholder%20farmers%2C%20the%20brand%20exported%2010%20tonnes%20of%20its%20produce%20to%20London%2C%20Canada%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20Kuwait%20by%20air.%20More%20exports%20meant%20more%20profits%20and%20happier%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20bitter%20tale%20behind%20the%20sweet%20tidings%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETejas%20grew%20up%20relishing%20Alphonsos%2C%20locally%20called%20%3Cem%3EHapus%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20on%20his%20two-acre%20farm.%20While%20savouring%20the%20sweet%20fruit%2C%20he%20also%20saw%20what%20went%20behind%20cultivating%20this%20popular%20fruit%20variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20my%20father%20toiling%20in%20the%20field.%20The%20process%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fmango-farmer-maharashtra-kakasaheb-sawant-kesar-hapus-chikoo-custard-apple-earns-crore%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20%3Cem%3EHapus%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20cumbersome.%20In%20our%20region%2C%20the%20soil%20is%20mainly%20lateritic%20and%20rocky%2C%20and%20mangoes%20are%20grown%20under%20rain-fed%20conditions.%20My%20father%20would%20first%20break%20the%20rocky%20soil%20and%20make%20the%20field%20favourable%20for%20mango%20plantation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20fruiting%20started%2C%20he%20would%20be%20out%20all%20day%20in%20summer%20heat%20protecting%20them%20from%20monkey%20attacks.%20If%20you%20are%20out%20of%20sight%20for%20even%20a%20few%2