oitation%20in%20this%20industry.%20Middlemen%20would%20sell%20our%20produce%20for%20Rs%20800-900%20per%20dozen%20but%20the%20growers%20would%20get%20only%20Rs%20200.%20We%20were%20being%20cheated%20and%20this%20has%20been%20in%20place%20for%20generations!%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028-year-old%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20that%20put%20an%20end%20to%20this%20age-old%20agony.%20%E2%80%9COnce%2C%20while%20watching%20the%20news%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20that%20Maharashtra%20only%20exports%20five%20percent%20of%20its%20Alphonsos%20whereas%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20bulk%20produce%20is%20consumed%20in%20the%20state%20itself.%20After%20studying%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20we%20could%20earn%20handsomely%20if%20we%20entered%20the%20export%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20consulting%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20farmers%2C%20Tejas%20went%20on%20to%20form%20Konkan%20Ratnagiri%20Boomi%20Agro%20Producer%20Limited%2C%20which%20was%20formally%20launched%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20small%20farmers%20unite%20against%20big%20players%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEntering%20the%20export%20business%20was%20a%20bold%20step%20for%20small%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20it%20was%20difficult%20to%20understand%20flight%20bookings%2C%20transportation%2C%20various%20kinds%20of%20food%20licences%2C%20and%20MRL%20(maximum%20residue%20level)%20tests%20for%20crops.%20As%20local%20farmers%2C%20we%20lacked%20that%20much%20knowledge%20and%20awareness.%20Many%20farmers%20feared%20and%20doubted%20their%20capabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tejas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FAamore-3-1718354958.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20farmers%20were%20able%20to%20earn%20up%