0seen%2016%2C344%20suspected%20heatstroke%20cases%20since%201%20March%20this%20year%2C%20with%20486%20suspected%20heatstroke%20cases%20on%2022%20May%20alone.%E2%80%9D%20Another%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%20%3C%2Fem%3Epointed%20out%20that%20in%20Ahmedabad%20alone%2C%20the%20city%20recorded%2045%20cases%20of%20heat%20strokes%20last%20summer%20with%20no%20comprehensive%20data%20on%20heat-related%20deaths.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20home%20solutions%20like%20dampening%20the%20curtains%20of%20their%20entrances%20and%20throwing%20water%20to%20cool%20down%20the%20roof%20worked%2C%20they%20all%20were%20temporary%20fixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20situation%20into%20careful%20consideration%2C%20an%20organisation%20called%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT)%20came%20up%20with%20a%20simple%20solution%20to%20the%20slum%E2%80%99s%20heat%20woes.%20If%20you%20now%20look%20at%20the%20roofs%20of%20most%20of%20these%20homes%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F106622%2Fmahesh-desai-helpline-education-home-ahmedabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20slums%20of%20Ahmedabad%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view%2C%20you%20will%20find%20them%20all%20painted%20in%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint%20so%20as%20to%20cool%20the%20indoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMHT%20representatives%20came%20to%20us%20and%20told%20us%20about%20the%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint.%20We%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20a%20reasonable%20thing%20to%20do.%20After%20painting%20our%20roof%20white%2C%20we%20noticed%20a%20significant%20improvement%20in%20the%20temperature%20inside%20our%20house.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20unbearably%20hot%2C%20but%20now%2C%20it%20feels%20much%20more%20comfortable%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Radha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20I%20am%20at%20work%2C%20my%20mother%20stays%20at%20home%20all%20day%2C%20and%20she%20also%20feels%20much%20better%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20slum%20dwellers%20survive%20the%20heatwave%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavna%20Maheriya%2C%20MHT%E2%80%99s%20programme%20manager%2C%20shares%20about%20the%20living%20conditions%20of%20slum%20dwellers.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20main%20concern%20at%20this%20point%20is%20to%20survive.%20Even%20if%20it%20is%2050%20degrees%20outside%20and%20the%20Government%20issues%20warnings%20of%20a%20heatwave%2C%20they%20have%20to%20go%20out%20and%20earn%20their%20food%20for%20the%20night.%20Heat%20action%20is%20their%20last%20priority%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20has%20helped%20women%20in%20slums%20bring%20down%20the%20temperatures%20in%20their%20homes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353028%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20has%20helped%20women%20in%20slums%20bring%20down%20the%20temperatures%20in%20their%20homes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20heat%20is%20so%20much%2C%20the%20rooms%20heat%20up%20too%2C%20becoming%20hotter%20than%20outside%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20proper%20ventilation%2C%20she%20shares.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20care%20of%20the%20heat%2C%20it%20becomes%20our%20duty%20to%20do%20it%20for%20them.%20The%20trust%20works%20in%20different%20areas%20and%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20initiatives%20that%20we%20have%20taken%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20started%20as%20a%20pilot%20in%202016%20when%20the%20trust%20was%20looking%20into%20cheaper%20and%20innovative%20ways%20of%20reducing%20heat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20organisation%20has%20been%20working%20in%20different%20areas%20such%20as%20pollution%2C%20climate%20change%2C%20etc%20for%20almost%2030%20years.%20In%202010%2C%20we%20started%20working%20for%20efficient%20energy%20and%20helped%20a%20lot%20of%20rural%20people%20in%20Ahmedabad%20have%20legal%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%20they%20used%20to%20get%20electricity%20illegally%20from%20poles%20or%20from%20someone%20else%E2%80%99s%20connection%20by%20paying%20them%20a%20small%20amount.%20This%20was%20illegal%20and%20highly%20dangerous.%20However%2C%20once%20the%20people%20switched%20to%20legal%20connections%20with%20authorised%20metres%2C%20the%20bills%20started%20to%20flow%20in.%20Most%20of%20the%20people%20complained%20about%20high%20electricity%20bills%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20MHT%20team%20inspected%20the%20homes%20of%20these%20people%20and%20realised%20that%20they%20were%20using%20100-watt%20bulbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20small%20home%20with%20one%20or%20two%20rooms%2C%20high%20bills%20are%20not%20possible.%20We%20noticed%20that%20the%20homes%20did%20not%20have%20proper%20ventilation%20due%20to%20shared%20walls.%20They%20have%20the%20kitchen%20in%20the%20same%20rooms%2C%20which%20also%20contributed%20to%20increasing%20the%20heat%20inside%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reduce%20the%20heat%2C%20people%20used%20to%20run%20fans%20and%20coolers%20the%20entire%20day%20at%20full%20speed%2C%20increasing%20the%20bill.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20made%20us%20realise%20that%20changing%20their%20bulbs%20would%20not%20solve%20the%20problem.%20We%20needed%20a%20heat%20action%20plan%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20UV%20reflective%20paint%20not%20only%20brings%20down%20the%20temperature%20but%20also%20reduces%20electricity%20bills%20due%20to%20less%20usage.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-3-1718282525-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353026%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20UV%20reflective%20paint%20not%20only%20brings%20down%20the%20temperature%20but%20also%20reduces%20electricity%20bills%20due%20to%20lesser%20usage.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20ray%20of%20relief%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavna%20takes%20us%20through%20the%20various%20pilots%20and%20schemes%20it%20launched%20before%20the%20UV%20white%20paint%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20introduced%20initiatives%20which%20modified%20their%20roofs.%20We%20introduced%20a%20fibre%20sheet%20roof%2C%20placed%20in%20a%20dome%20style%20with%20a%20%3Cem%3Ejaali%20%3C%2Fem%3Estructure%20for%20ventilation.%20This%20not%20only%20improved%20the%20ventilation%20but%20also%20reduced%20the%20heat.%20This%20plan%20became%20very%20popular%20and%20we%20installed%20it%20in%20nearly%20500%20homes.%20In%202013%2C%20we%20introduced%20another%20pilot%20called%20modular%20roofs.%20The%20reduction%20in%20temperature%20was%20five%20to%20six%20degrees%20but%20the%20product%20needed%20a%20lot%20of%20modifications%20in%20the%20existing%20structure%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20had%20pilots%20like%20thermocol%20false%20ceilings%20and%20bamboo%20ceilings%20too.%20It%20was%20in%202016%20that%20we%20introduced%20the%20rooftop%20white%20paint.%20The%20paint%20reduced%20the%20temperature%20by%20five%20to%20six%20degrees%20inside%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20the%20cool%20roof%20technology%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20best%20thing%20about%20this%20initiative%20was%20that%20the%20application%20was%20very%20easy.%20The%20women%20could%20easily%20source%20it%20from%20us%20and%20apply%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20Ahmedabad%20Heat%20Action%20Plan%20committee%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20to%20understand%20how%20the%20cool%20roof%20technology%20works.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20included%20our%20cool%20roof%20technology%20in%20their%20revised%20plan%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20various%20initiatives%20are%20launched%2C%20many%20steps%20are%20taken%20to%20ensure%20they%20benefit%20the%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20are%20structural%20changes%20in%20the%20homes%20of%20slum%20dwellers%2C%20we%20give%20them%20a%20100%20percent%20guarantee%20that%20if%20the%20technology%20does%20not%20suit%20them%2C%20we%20will%20reverse%20all%20the%20changes%20made%20to%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20over%2020%2C000%20slum%20homes%20in%20Ahmedabad%20have%20benefitted%20from%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20women%20in%20slum%20areas%20are%20given%20proper%20induction%20before%20a%20project%20is%20implemented%20in%20their%20homes.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-2-1718282527-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353027%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20women%20in%20slum%20areas%20are%20given%20proper%20induction%20before%20a%20project%20is%20implemented%20in%20their%20homes.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20learned%20about%20this%20white%20paint%20and%20its%20benefits%20during%20a%20Community%20Action%20Group%20(CAG)%20meeting%20supported%20by%20the%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%20(MHT).%20They%20gave%20us%20a%20poster%20that%20had%20details%20about%20the%20solar%20reflective%20white%20paint.%20We%20understood%20that%20it%20helps%20reduce%20the%20heat%20inside%20our%20houses%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20house%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20proper%20ventilation.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20so%20hot%20during%20the%20summer%20that%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20sit%20inside%20comfortably.%20But%20after%20we%20applied%20the%20paint%20on%20our%20roof%2C%20it%20feels%20much%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suman%20who%20lived%20in%20the%20Ignas%20Park%20slum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20trust%20depends%20on%20funds%20and%20contributions%20to%20continue%20helping%20the%20people%20living%20in%20slums%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3xicHzY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20how%20you%20can%20help%20them.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20images%20credit%3A%20Mahila%20Housing%20Trust)%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718284321000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fmht-1-1718282529.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D353012%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mahila%20Housing%20Trust%2C%20an%20organisation%20dedicated%20to%20assisting%20women%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%2C%20is%20using%20cool%20roof%20technology%20to%20help%20them%20escape%20the%20heat%20in%20Ahmedabad.%20This%20initiative%20has%20made%20over%2020%2C000%20homes%20cooler%20and%20more%20comfortable%20during%20the%20heatwave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Things%20The%20New%20Govt%20Must%20Do%20to%20Make%20Development%20Sustainable%20%26amp%3B%20Work%20For%20the%20Planet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Government%20must%20rebuild%20trust%20by%20being%20tolerant%20to%20ideas%2C%20opinions%20and%20information.%20It%20needs%20to%20strengthen%20ground-level%20institutions%20because%20participatory%20democracy%20can%20ensure%20development%20delivery.%20In%20this%20age%20of%20climate%20risk%2C%20the%20Government%20also%20needs%20to%20re-engineer%20development%20to%20make%20it%20inclusive%2C%20affordable%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agenda%20for%20the%20new%20Government%20is%20the%20old%20one%2C%20but%20with%20a%20fundamental%20difference.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20the%20list%20of%20priority%20action%20areas%20remains%20the%20same.%20We%20have%20unfinished%20business%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20virtually%20everything%E2%80%94from%20energy%20to%20water%20and%20sanitation%20to%20food%20and%20nutrition%20to%2C%20of%20course%2C%20health%20and%20education.%20We%20know%20that%20the%20Government%20has%20schemes%20in%20place%20and%20budgets%20allocated%20for%20all%20these%20issues.%20We%20also%20know%20that%20ensuring%20the%20welfare%20and%20well-being%20of%20people%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20election%2C%20as%20journalists%20fanned%20out%20to%20listen%20to%20the%20opinions%20of%20voters%E2%80%94perhaps%20the%20only%20time%20when%20their%20opinions%20count%E2%80%94we%20heard%20that%20unemployment%20is%20a%20major%20concern%3B%20lack%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335025%2Fclean-drinking-water-from-thin-air-scientists-breakthrough-revolutionises-access-to-pure-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclean%20drinking%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sanitation%20tops%20the%20agenda%3B%20the%20energy%20crisis%20is%20still%20wicked%20as%20the%20price%20of%20the%20LPG%20cylinder%20is%20unaffordable%20and%20electricity%20unreliable.%20Farmers%20are%20still%20distressed.%20So%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20still%20needs%20to%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20should%20not%20come%20as%20a%20surprise.%20India%20is%20a%20vast%20country%2C%20with%20a%20massive%20deficit%20in%20governance.%20The%20last%20mile%20for%20any%20government%20scheme%20is%20about%20making%20sure%20that%20it%20reaches%20people%E2%80%94not%20once%20but%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20seeing%20the%20impact%20of%20climate%20change.%20Our%20data%20shows%20that%20every%20day%2C%20some%20or%20the%20other%20part%20of%20the%20country%20is%20being%20battered%20by%20at%20least%20one%20extreme%20weather%20event.%20This%20has%20huge%20implications%20for%20development%20programmes%E2%80%94unseasonal%20and%20extreme%20weather%20lead%20to%20more%20droughts%2C%20floods%20and%20loss%20of%20livelihoods%2C%20putting%20additional%20strain%20on%20the%20resources%20of%20the%20government.%20This%20means%20that%20development%20will%20need%20to%20be%20more%20efficient%20and%20delivered%20at%20scale%20and%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20all%20this%20to%20change%20and%20more%2C%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20new%20agenda%20and%20must%20be%20different%20in%20the%20following%20respects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20it%20must%20be%20based%20on%20rebuilding%20institutions%20for%20increased%20feedback%20and%20accountability.%20Anybody%20who%20has%20a%20differing%20perspective%20is%20not%20an%20enemy%20of%20the%20state.%20Alternative%20information%20is%20not%20dissent%20or%20targeted%20criticism%20of%20the%20Government.%20These%20sources%20of%20news%20and%20analysis%20must%20be%20seen%20as%20part%20of%20the%20tapestry%20of%20development.%20The%20more%20we%20learn%20about%20what%20is%20working%20and%20what%20is%20not%2C%20the%20more%20governance%20improves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20most%20differing%20voices%20have%20been%20silenced%E2%80%94perhaps%20not%20deliberately%20but%20through%20the%20unsaid%20that%20makes%20it%20more%20acceptable%20to%20be%20acceptable%20if%20you%20have%20things%20that%20the%20powers%20want%20to%20hear.%20It%20is%20like%20an%20echo%20chamber%20where%20only%20cheerleaders%20thrive.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20this%20only%20makes%20a%20government%20poorer%E2%80%94they%20hear%20nothing%20and%20learn%20little.%20So%2C%20the%20agenda%20for%20the%20Government%20is%20to%20be%20open%E2%80%94this%20is%20not%20about%20inclusion%20in%20government%20committee%20rooms%20but%20in%20the%20tolerance%20of%20information%2C%20ideas%20and%20opinions.%20Rebuilding%20trust%20is%20key%E2%80%94not%20just%20for%20schemes%20to%20succeed%20but%20also%20for%20societies%20to%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20we%20need%20institutions%20for%20new%20India.%20Over%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20most%20conventional%20institutions%20have%20been%20deliberately%2C%20or%20by%20sheer%20neglect%2C%20allowed%20to%20decay.%20The%20reason%2C%20the%20Government%20may%20tell%20you%2C%20is%20that%20these%20agencies%20were%20not%20doing%20their%20jobs%20well%3B%20they%20needed%20to%20go.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20nothing%20has%20been%20done%20to%20replace%20the%20key%20functions%20that%20these%20institutions%20are%20required%20to%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20case%20of%20agencies%20set%20up%20to%20control%20pollution.%20They%20have%20become%20mute%20and%20meaningless.%20Maybe%20because%20when%20they%20had%20power%2C%20some%20indulged%20in%20making%20money%20from%20the%20business%20of%20combating%20pollution.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20combating%20pollution%20needs%20institutions%20that%20can%20apply%20deterrence%20with%20accountability%20and%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20navigate%20inconvenient%20and%20tough%20decisions.%20This%20is%20completely%20missing%20today.%20So%2C%20it%20should%20not%20surprise%20us%20that%20we%20have%20more%20pollution%2C%20not%20less%2C%20all%20across%20our%20rivers%20and%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20to%20change%2C%20we%20need%20two%20next-generation%20reforms.%20One%2C%20we%20need%20to%20strengthen%20the%20ground-level%20institutions%2C%20where%20local%20people%20take%20part.%20We%20need%20participatory%20democracy%20to%20make%20development%20programmes%20work.%20It%20is%20now%20over%2030%20years%20since%20the%20country%20passed%20the%2074th%20and%2075th%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%20to%20empower%20people%E2%80%99s%20institutions%E2%80%94the%20Panchayati%20Raj%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%20the%20municipal%20system%20for%20urban%20India.%20We%20have%20also%20experimented%20with%20deepening%20democracy%20through%20the%20strengthening%20of%20gram%20sabhas%E2%80%94village%20assemblies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20this%20is%20unfinished%20work.%20We%20have%20much%20more%20to%20do%20to%20give%20control%20over%20natural%20resources%20to%20village%20and%20City%20Governments.%20We%20need%20them%20to%20manage%20funds%20and%20schemes%3B%20to%20create%20green%20jobs%3B%20to%20invest%20in%20natural%20resources%20for%20livelihoods.%20We%20need%20to%20celebrate%20the%20noise%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20we%20need%20imagination%20in%20the%20design%20of%20development%20schemes.%20For%20too%20long%2C%20governments%20have%20been%20caught%20between%20the%20welfare%20approach%E2%80%94which%20is%20often%20dismissed%20as%20the%20handout%E2%80%94and%20the%20capitalistic%20minimum%20approach.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328522%2Fhow-nature-based-solutions-can-help-build-climate-change-resilience-wri-projects%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eage%20of%20climate%20risk%3C%2Fa%3E%20needs%20a%20new%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20needs%20to%20rework%20and%20re-engineer%20development%20so%20that%20it%20is%20inclusive%2C%20affordable%20and%2C%20thus%2C%20sustainable.%20This%20means%20reimagining%20the%20way%20we%20work%20in%20almost%20every%20sphere%E2%80%94from%20the%20supply%20of%20clean%20water%2C%20so%20that%20it%20is%20not%20resource-%20or%20capital-intensive%2C%20to%20the%20access%20to%20energy%20so%20that%20it%20is%20clean%20but%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20affordable.%20This%20will%20require%20changes%20in%20design%20and%20then%20in%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20need%20a%20new%20development%20paradigm%20that%20can%20work%20for%20the%20Planet%2C%20but%20for%20this%2C%20it%20needs%20to%20work%20for%20every%20last%20person.%20This%2C%20then%2C%20is%20where%20we%20need%20the%20focus%20and%20attention%20of%20the%20old-new%20Government.%20This%20is%20our%20common%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fenvironment%2Fworld-environment-day-2024-india-needs-new-imagination-in-design-of-its-development-schemes-says-sunita-narain-96525%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%40down2earthindia%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Published%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20with%20permission.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%40down2earthindia%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718255431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352906%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%20Government%20must%20rebuild%20trust%20by%20being%20tolerant%20to%20ideas%2C%20opinions%20and%20information.%20It%20needs%20to%20strengthen%20ground-level%20institutions%20because%20participatory%20democracy%20can%20ensure%20development%20delivery.%20In%20this%20age%20of%20climate%20risk%2C%20the%20Government%20also%20needs%20to%20re-engineer%20development%20to%20make%20it%20inclusive%2C%20affordable%20and%20sustainable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sunita%20Narain%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Real%20Story%20Behind%20Netflix%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Maharaj%E2%80%99%3A%20When%20a%20Reporter%20Took%20On%20a%20%E2%80%98Messiah%E2%80%99%20To%20Uncover%20the%20Truth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20high-tension%20courtroom%20filled%20to%20the%20brim%20with%20onlookers%20keenly%20observing%20every%20move%20of%20the%20judges.%20The%20key%20players%20are%20a%20journalist%20and%20a%20renowned%20godman%20facing%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20assault.%20Sounds%20like%20a%20thriller%2C%20right%3F%20What%20if%20we%20told%20you%20this%20actually%20happened%20in%20the%201800s%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFilmmaker%20Siddharth%20P%20Malhotra%E2%80%99s%20upcoming%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F289718%2Fwhat-to-watch-on-netflix-amazon-prime-sony-liv-latest-release%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperiod%20drama%20on%20Netflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20%E2%80%98Maharaj%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Starring%20Junaid%20Khan%2C%20Jaideep%20Ahlawat%2C%20Sharvari%20Wagh%2C%20and%20Shalini%20Pandey%20%E2%80%94%20is%20based%20on%20a%20similar%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentred%20on%20the%20Maharaj%20Libel%20Case%20of%201862%20in%20the%20Bombay%20High%20Court%2C%20the%20film%20highlights%20the%20efforts%20of%20real-life%20journalist%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20to%20expose%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20misconduct%20of%20religious%20leader%20Jadunathji%20Brijratanji%20Maharaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Joseph%20Arnould%20ruled%20in%20favour%20of%20Karsandas%2C%20making%20it%20sensational%20news%20at%20the%20time.%20In%20the%20words%20of%20Arnould%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20public%20journalist%20is%20a%20public%20teacher%3A%20the%20true%20function%20of%20the%20press%2C%20that%20by%20virtue%20of%20which%20it%20has%20rightly%20grown%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20great%20powers%20of%20the%20modern%20world%E2%80%94is%20the%20function%20of%20teaching%2C%20elevating%20and%20enlightening%20those%20who%20fall%20within%20the%20range%20of%20its%20influence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20who%20was%20this%20brave%20journalist%2C%20and%20why%20did%20he%20involve%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F235308%2Fsupreme-court-daughters-sons-equal-right-property-coparcener-mishra-mary-roy-arundhati-educationist-hindu-succession-act-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehimself%20in%20a%20legal%20battle%20%3C%2Fa%3Eagainst%20the%20%E2%80%98Maharaj%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20here%20is%20a%20bite%20of%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20public%20servant%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201832%20to%20a%20family%20of%20the%20Kapol%20Caste%2C%20a%20trading%20caste%20of%20Western%20India%2C%20Karsandas%20was%20always%20dedicated%20to%20public%20service.%20He%20was%20an%20active%20member%20of%20the%20Gujarati%20Gnanprasarak%20Mandalli%20(Gujarati%20Society%20for%20the%20Spread%20of%20Knowledge)%2C%20founded%20by%20the%20Students%E2%80%99%20Society%20of%20Elphinstone%20College.%20Among%20his%20classmates%20were%20prominent%20reformers%20such%20as%20poet%20Narmad%20and%20educationist%20Mahipatram%20Neelkanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20article%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%201851%2C%20he%20penned%20an%20essay%20for%20a%20literary%20competition%2C%20advocating%20for%20widow%20remarriage.%20When%20the%20news%20reached%20Karsandas%E2%80%99%20elderly%20aunt%2C%20who%20had%20cared%20for%20him%20following%20his%20mother%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20she%20promptly%20evicted%20him%20from%20her%20home.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Karsandas%20was%20married.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20neither%20society%20nor%20familial%20pressure%20could%20stop%20Karsandas%20from%20following%20his%20journalistic%20instincts.%20Wanting%20to%20be%20more%20free%20with%20his%20writing%20and%20ideas%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20start%20his%20own%20magazine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20some%20friends%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F171267%2Fmadurai-gandhi-iconic-dress-loincloth-freedom-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20started%20a%20Gujarati%20weekly%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20around%201855%20called%20%3Cem%3ESatyaprakash%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20further%20his%20work%20of%20social%20interest.%20The%20weekly%20magazine%20was%20known%20for%20boldly%20confronting%20outdated%20Indian%20traditions%20and%20societal%20evils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-500x561.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Netflix%20Film%20Maharaj%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-500x561.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-268x300.jpg%20268w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040-150x168.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FScreenshot-2024-06-12-184745-2-1718203040.jpg%20504w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352922%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENetflix%20Film%20Maharaj%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Cem%3EIndianliberals.in%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20paper%20had%20a%20meagre%20subscription%20of%20500%2C%20yet%20its%20impact%20on%20Bombay%E2%80%99s%20conservative%20Gujarati%20Hindu%20community%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20overstated.%20In%20the%201850s%2C%20he%20went%20on%20to%20edit%20a%20series%20of%20newspapers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Pushtimarg%20sect%20and%20Maharaj%E2%80%99s%20role%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarsandas%20was%20a%20follower%20of%20the%20Pushtimarg%20sect%2C%20founded%20by%20Vallabhacharya%20in%20the%2016th%20century%2C%20a%20prominent%20Hindu%20devotional%20sect%20in%20western%20India.%20By%20the%2019th%20century%2C%20Pushtimarg%20had%20amassed%20significant%20wealth%20and%20influence%2C%20with%20its%20spiritual%20leaders%2C%20known%20as%20Maharajs%2C%20wielding%20considerable%20power%20over%20their%20followers.%20These%20leaders%20were%20revered%20as%20living%20incarnations%20of%20Krishna%20and%20enjoyed%20a%20lavish%20lifestyle%20supported%20by%20the%20donations%20of%20devotees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Maharajas%20often%20faced%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20impropriety%20and%20corruption%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20growing%20rift%20between%20traditionalists%20and%20reform-minded%20individuals%20by%20the%20late%201800s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20himself%20also%20started%20to%20question%20the%20viability%20of%20the%20faith%20through%20his%20writings.%20In%201861%2C%20he%20published%20an%20article%20titled%20%3Cem%3EHinduono%20Asal%20Dharma%20ane%20Haalna%20Pakhandi%20Mato%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20Primitive%20Religion%20of%20the%20Hindus%20and%20the%20Present%20Heterodox%20Opinions)%2C%20which%20delivered%20the%20heaviest%20blow%20on%20the%20Maharaj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20charges%2C%20it%20accused%20them%20of%20having%20sexual%20alliances%20with%20their%20female%20devotees.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20led%20to%20the%20Maharaj%20filing%20the%20famous%20libel%20case%20in%20the%20Bombay%20court%3B%20it%20was%20called%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgreatest%20trial%20of%20modern%20times%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1057%2F9780230306004_2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrial%20of%20Warren%20Hastings%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20paper%20posted%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20University%20of%20Toronto%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20article%20in%20question%20not%20only%20denounced%20the%20Pushtimarg%20as%20heterodox%2C%20a%20latter-day%20corruption%20of%20the%20original%20Vedic%20religion%3B%20it%20also%20specifically%20accused%20Jadunathji%20of%20imposing%20himself%20sexually%20on%20his%20female%20devotees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJadunathji%20Brijratanji%20Maharaj%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20worth%20Rs%2050%2C000%20against%20Karsandas%20for%20harming%20his%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20historic%20ruling%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharaj%20might%20have%20hoped%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F159978%2Fabortion-india-rules-how-to-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBombay%20Supreme%20Court%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewould%20clear%20his%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20name%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20he%20was%20sorely%20mistaken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20of%20the%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20held%20before%20a%20full%20court%2C%20presided%20over%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20Mathew%20Sausse%20and%20Joseph%20Arnould.%20The%20case%20attracted%20significant%20interest%20from%20the%20press%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20members%20of%20the%20public%20attended%20the%20court%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-14-1718203149-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352925%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20Karsandas%20Mulji%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarsandas%20who%20belonged%20to%20the%20same%20community%20faced%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20and%20was%20threatened%20to%20be%20excommunicated.%20%E2%80%9CThirty-one%20witnesses%20for%20the%20plaintiff%20and%20thirty-three%20witnesses%20for%20the%20defendants%20were%20examined%3B%20Jadunath%20Maharaj%20was%20brought%20to%20court%2C%20which%20ultimately%20dismissed%20his%20defamation%20charges%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20the%20sect%E2%80%99s%20philosophies%20were%20examined%20and%20compared%20with%20other%20Hindu%20texts%20by%20missionary%20orientalist%20scholars%20and%20philosophers%20like%20John%20Wilson.%20Doctors%2C%20including%20Bhau%20Daji%20who%20was%20a%20known%20Indian%20physician%2C%20Sanskrit%20scholar%20and%20an%20antiquarian%2C%20testified%20that%20they%20had%20treated%20the%20religious%20leader%20for%20syphilis%2C%20and%20several%20witnesses%20recounted%20his%20erotic%20escapades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20featured%20dramatic%20testimonies%20from%20various%20witnesses%2C%20including%20women%20who%20claimed%20to%20have%20been%20exploited%20by%20the%20Maharaj.%20These%20testimonies%20were%20crucial%20in%20substantiating%20Karsandas%E2%80%99%20allegations%20and%20painted%20a%20stark%20picture%20of%20the%20abuses%20of%20power%20within%20the%20sect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20came%20to%20a%20close%20on%2022%20April%2C%201862%2C%20with%20a%20judgment%20in%20favour%20of%20Karsandas%20Mulji.%20The%20court%20awarded%20him%20Rs%2011%2C500%2C%20as%20he%20had%20to%20bear%20a%20total%20expenditure%20of%20Rs%2014%2C000%20during%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClosing%20the%20case%20Judge%20Arnould%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20not%20a%20question%20of%20theology%20that%20has%20been%20before%20us!%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20morality.%20The%20principle%20for%20which%20the%20defendant%20and%20his%20witnesses%20have%20been%20contending%20is%20si