l-Paani-2-1718112270-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270-500x334.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-2-1718112270-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352673%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManaging%20Water%20Treatment%20Infrastructure%3A%20Mansi%20Jain%2C%20co-founder%20of%20Digital%20Paani%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBut%20why%20do%20these%20facilities%20fail%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mansi%2C%20most%20of%20these%20plants%20don%E2%80%99t%20work%20in%20the%20long%20run%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons%20including%20biological%20disturbance%2C%20equipment%20failure%20like%20burnt%20pumps%2C%20or%20the%20choking%20of%20membrane%20filters%20that%20act%20as%20a%20barrier%20to%20separate%20contaminants%20from%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20there%20a%20way%20for%20these%20plants%20to%20anticipate%20these%20problems%20and%20fix%20them%20in%20advance%20to%20improve%20their%20efficiency%20and%20longevity%3F%20Suffice%20it%20to%20say%20that%20there%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Ftopics%2Fstartup%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%20that%20are%20developing%20technological%20solutions%20for%20wastewater%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20about%2090%2C000%20installed%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants.%20But%20today%2095%25%20of%20the%20market%20is%20managed%20entirely%20manually%20by%20deploying%20operators%20in%20each%20plant.%20This%20has%20several%20drawbacks%3B%20problems%20are%20detected%20abou