2wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20Digital%20Paani%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20%E2%80%9Cintegrates%20every%20aspect%20of%20wastewater%20treatment%20operations%20and%20scales%20the%20expertise%20needed%20to%20handle%20facilities%E2%80%9D%20in%20three%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20First%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98knows%E2%80%99%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20plants%20by%20determining%20how%20each%20facility%20should%20operate%20given%20its%20unique%20physical%20configuration%20and%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20this%20by%20doing%20a%20design%20assessment%20of%20each%20facility%20on%20our%20software%20as%20well%20as%20capturing%20operations%20information%20from%20each%20unit%20operation%20in%20a%20facility.%20This%20data%20spans%20a%20wide%20range%2C%20from%20using%20computer%20vision%20to%20look%20at%20biological%20process%20health%2C%20to%20looking%20at%20electrical%20data%2C%20energy%20data%2C%20pressure%2C%20vibration%2C%20flow%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mansi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20Second%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98tells%E2%80%99%20the%20need%20to%20the%20relevant%20stakeholders%20by%20offering%20complete%20visibility%20through%20WhatsApp%20and%20live%20dashboards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20Finally%2C%20it%20%E2%80%98solves%E2%80%99%20the%20need%20by%20executing%20the%20required%20actions%20directly%20through%20automated%20workflows%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20training%20onsite%20teams%2C%20guiding%20their%20daily%20workflow%20and%20validating%20their%20work%20or%20managing%20the%20physical%20operation%20of%20equipment%20through%20our%20in-platform%20automation%20manager.%20When%20things%20start%20going%20wrong%2C%20it%20uses%20data%20streams%20from%20onsite%20sensors%20and%20electrical%20panels%20to%20diagnose%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20drive%20issue%20closure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20even%20recommend%20operational%20and%20physical%20improvements.%20This%20approach%20has%20transformed%20defunct%20facilities%20while%20reducing%20their%20costs%20by%20up%20to%2066%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Here's%20how%20you%20can%20do%20water%20treatment%20with%20Digital%20Paani%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Worker-and-Software-1718112556-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352680%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDigital%20Paani%20looks%20to%20understand%20the%20physical%20water%20treatment%20infrastructure%20and%20develops%20unique%20tools%20to%20manage%20it.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20do%20industry%20giants%20use%20Digital%20Paani%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMansi%20argues%20that%20every%20building%20and%20factory%20can%20rely%20on%20local%20and%20renewable%20wastewater%20for%20up%20to%2090%25%20of%20their%20water%20needs%2C%20a%20vital%20response%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346640%2Fbengaluru-water-scarcity-crisis-solutions-lake-revival-open-wells-rainwater-harvesting-treated-wastewater%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20water%20scarcity%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20climate%20change.%20Unfortunately%2C%20as%20she%20stated%20earlier%20in%20this%20article%2C%20about%2075%25%20of%20treatment%20facilities%20end%20up%20dysfunctional%20because%20operations%20are%20manual%20and%20reactive%2C%20and%20the%20expertise%20and%20skills%20needed%20to%20manage%20such%20complex%20operations%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%20at%20the%20ground%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99re%20solving%20the%20above%20issue%20by%20reimagining%20this%20industry%20through%20Digital%20Paani%2C%20which%20effectively%20scales%20the%20needed%20technical%20expertise%20to%20drive%20operational%20excellence%20in%20facilities.%20This%20results%20in%20the%20transformation%20of%20non%20or%20low-functioning%20plants%20to%20high-quality%2C%20compliant%20units%20treating%20100%25%20of%20water%20to%20high-water-quality%20standards%2C%20all%20while%20reducing%20operating%20costs%20by%20up%20to%2030%25.%20Many%20of%20our%20customers%20have%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20breakdowns%20significantly%20(up%20to%2085%25)%20and%20reduce%20energy%20consumption%20in%20the%20range%20of%2020%20to%2035%25%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20importantly%2C%20they%20can%20now%20confidently%20reuse%20this%20water%3B%20many%20of%20our%20customers%20have%20gone%20from%20reusing%2045%25%20of%20their%20water%20on%20average%20to%20around%2080%25.%20This%20is%20why%20major%20players%20in%20the%20industry%20are%20adopting%20our%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20as%20Mansi%20notes%2C%20the%20ease%20of%20integrating%20Digital%20Paani%2C%20which%20functions%20on%20a%20plug-and-play%20model%2C%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20enhances%20its%20appeal%E2%80%9D.%20Treatment%20facilities%20of%20any%20size%20and%20type%20can%20be%20installed%20in%20three%20straightforward%20steps%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20Site%20survey%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20%5BParallel%5D%20Any%20IoT%20deployment%20needed%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3)%20%5BParallel%5D%20Plant%20onboarding%20onto%20our%20software%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20whole%20process%20only%20takes%2030%20to%2045%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20industries%2C%20Digital%20Paani%20has%20also%20made%20forays%20into%20the%20residential%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20provide%20continuous%20expertise%20for%20regular%20operations%20as%20well%20as%20guidance%20on%20the%20needed%20retrofits%20so%20that%20they%20can%20get%20their%20STP%20completely%20streamlined%20and%20treat%20and%20reuse%20their%20water.%20We%20have%20converted%20many%20residential%20STPs%20from%20dysfunctional%20to%20reusing%2070%25%20of%20water%20in%20flushing%2C%20horticulture%2C%20and%20more.%20Many%20customers%20used%20to%20receive%20notices%20and%20fines%20from%20the%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20earlier%20because%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20manage%20their%20operations%2C%20and%20we%20have%20solved%20that%20for%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAdaptable%20to%20different%20environments%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20software%20is%20highly%20flexible%2C%20featuring%20comprehensive%20configuration%20panels%20that%20simplify%20the%20integration%20of%20plants%20of%20different%20sizes%20and%20technologies.%20On%20the%20backend%2C%20we%20have%20onboarded%20each%20key%20unit%20operation%20in%20water%20management%2C%20be%20it%20biological%20treatment%2C%20chemical%20treatment%2C%20RO%20systems%2C%20UF%20systems%20or%20more%2C%20so%20when%20we%20onboard%20a%20new%20unit%2C%20we%20simply%20tick%20that%20module%20and%20get%20the%20relevant%20analytics%2C%20automation%20flows%2C%20alerts%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rajesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20adapt%20to%20facilities%20of%20all%20kinds.%20Moreover%2C%20our%20team%20is%20well-equipped%20to%20provide%20expert%20support%20for%20any%20plant%20management%20as%20required.%20For%20instance%2C%20at%20present%2C%20we%20serve%20diverse%20needs%20including%20STP%20management%20for%20Taj%20Hotels%2C%20ETP%20management%20for%20Britannia%2C%20total%20water%20management%20for%20Plaksha%20University%2C%20and%20a%2070%20MLD%20STP%20in%20Dwarka%2C%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mansi%20Jain%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20recently%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FDigital-Paani-Shark-Tank-India-1718112700-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352685%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMansi%20Jain%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20recently%20appeared%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPan-India%20presence%20and%20funding%20their%20ambition%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20currently%20operational%20in%20about%2014%20states%20and%20has%20raised%20about%20%241.2%20million%20from%20global%20investors%20like%20Elemental%20Excelerator%20and%20Echo%20River%20Capital%20as%20well%20as%20Indian%20investors%20like%20Enzia%2C%20Peer%20Cheque%2C%20SAE%2C%20DevC%2C%20Bharat%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20and%20leading%20angels%20like%20Ashish%20Goel%20(Urban%20Ladder)%2C%20Yamini%20Bhatt%20(Wymo)%20and%20Mohit%20Tandon%20(Delhivery).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Karuna%20Jain%20and%20Shivam%20Jindal%20of%20Enzia%20Ventures%2C%20a%20venture%20capital%20fund%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.enzia.vc%2Fperspective-posts%2Fwhy-we-invested-in-digital-paani%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esay%20about%20their%20decision%20to%20invest%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20startup%2C%20%E2%80%9CDigital%20Paani%E2%80%99s%20solution%20seamlessly%20integrates%20into%20existing%20facilities%2C%20analysing%20the%20infrastructure%E2%80%99s%20needs%20based%20on%20multiple%20performance%20parameters%2C%20making%20these%20needs%20transparent%20to%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20and%20solving%20for%20these%20needs%20by%20automating%20unit%20operations%20and%20managing%20all%20human%20workflows%20including%20training%2C%20SOPs%2C%20and%20troubleshooting.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20it%20helps%20ensure%20continuous%20and%20efficient%20operation%20of%20these%20plants%2C%20reducing%20energy%2C%20breakdown%2C%20manpower%2C%20and%20chemical%20costs%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20~25%20to%2035%25%20over%20current%20costs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20Paani%20is%20currently%20working%20with%20more%20than%2040%20wastewater%20treatment%20plants.%20In%20the%20previous%20financial%20year%20(2023-24)%20till%20February%202024%2C%20they%20earned%20revenues%20of%20Rs%202.2%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Mansi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20big%20ambition%20is%20to%20build%20the%20future%20of%20water%20and%20drive%20climate%20resilience%20by%20unlocking%20wastewater%E2%80%99s%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20key%20source%20of%20water%20globally.%20To%20do%20this%2C%20we%20intend%20to%20build%20the%20tech%20ecosystem%20for%20wastewater%20by%20not%20only%20working%20with%205%2C000%20facilities%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20to%20ensure%20they%20operate%20well%20but%20also%20creating%20data%20products%20that%20replace%20the%20consultant%20industry%20that%20drives%20infrastructure%20decisions%20with%20a%20more%20data-driven%20approach.%20We%20also%20intend%20to%20enable%20each%20building%20and%20factory%20to%20be%20water-neutral.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Rajesh%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20eventual%20vision%20is%20to%20create%20water-positive%20buildings%20and%20industries%20that%20in%20turn%20significantly%20improve%20quality%20of%20life%20in%20our%20cities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalpaani.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDigital%20Paani%3C%2Fa%3E%2FInstagram%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fpulse%2Fdigital-paani-making-watertech-work-alexander-hogeveen-rutter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%2FAlexander%20Hogeveen%20Rutter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBharatFounders%2Fstatus%2F1775471473580286296%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETwitter%2FBharat%20Founders%20Fund%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718116327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D352664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mansi%20Jain%2C%20a%20graduate%20of%20environmental%20economics%20from%20Stanford%20University%20and%20her%20father%20Rajesh%20Jain%2C%20a%20product%20of%20IIT-Delhi%2C%20founded%20their%20startup%20Digital%20Paani%20to%20help%20industries%20and%20residential%20societies%20treat%20their%20wastewater%20more%20efficiently%20and%20at%20a%20lower%20cost.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20This%20Farmer%E2%80%99s%20Patented%20Grow%20Bags%2C%20You%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Need%20to%20Worry%20About%20Watering%20Your%20Plants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20lush%20landscapes%20of%20Malabar%2C%20amidst%20sprawling%20coffee%2C%20cocoa%2C%20and%20rubber%20plantations%2C%20Eyyo%20Kuriakose%E2%80%99s%20passion%20for%20farming%20blossomed.%20Growing%20up%2C%20he%20spent%20countless%20hours%20assisting%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%20on%20their%20farm%2C%20an%20experience%20that%20sowed%20the%20seeds%20of%20a%20lifetime%20commitment%20to%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20at%2078%2C%20Eyyo%20has%20witnessed%20significant%20shifts%20in%20farming%20practices%2C%20driven%20by%20alarming%20changes%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331849%2Fgardening-dr-navdeep-singh-khurana-dentist-amritsar-flowers-vegetables-indoor-garden%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoil%20quality%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20increased%20pest%20attacks%2C%20which%20have%20impacted%20the%20quality%20and%20quantity%20of%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20observation%20kindled%20in%20Eyyo%20a%20deep%20interest%20in%20organic%20farming%2C%20pushing%20him%20to%20explore%20sustainable%20and%20healthier%20methods%20of%20crop%20cultivation.%20Unlike%20conventional%20practices%20that%20often%20rely%20heavily%20on%20chemical%20inputs%2C%20organic%20farming%20presents%20a%20harmonious%20alternative%2C%20promising%20a%20return%20to%20eco-friendly%20practices%20without%20sacrificing%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%E2%80%99s%20approach%20was%20always%20to%20stay%20abreast%20with%20the%20latest%20agricultural%20innovations%2C%20adapting%20and%20implementing%20new%20methods%20that%20could%20support%20the%20environment%20and%20yield%20healthy%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Kottayam%20resident%20made%20the%20switch%20to%20organic%20farming%20after%20relocating%20to%20Nedumkandam%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20avoid%20inorganic%20vegetables%20commonly%20available%20in%20markets.%20Starting%20with%20basic%20gardening%20using%20standard%20grow%20bags%2C%20he%20soon%20discovered%20the%20limitations%20of%20these%20products%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20prone%20to%20tearing%20and%20decayed%20within%20a%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20he%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20create%20a%20better%20grow%20bag%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20durable%20but%20also%20integrated%20a%20clever%20drip%20irrigation%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Eyyo's%20patented%20grow%20bags%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039-300x135.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039-500x225.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039-768x346.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-2-min-1718113039-150x68.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEyyo%E2%80%99s%20patented%20grow%20bags.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20efforts%20led%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20patented%20grow%20bag%20that%20claims%20to%20transform%20the%20way%20vegetables%20are%20grown.%20These%20specially%20designed%20bags%20require%20only%20two%20litres%20of%20water%20to%20nourish%20the%20plants%20effectively%2C%20making%20them%20not%20only%20water-efficient%20but%20also%20cost-effective.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20innovative%20design%20of%20these%20grow%20bags%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20bacterial%20and%20fungal%20infections%2C%20ensuring%20healthier%20plant%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20these%20durable%20grow%20bags%20could%20be%20significant%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20agriculture%20practices.%20By%20reducing%20water%20usage%20and%20enhancing%20the%20longevity%20of%20the%20grow%20materials%2C%20these%20bags%20represent%20a%20step%20forward%20in%20solving%20some%20of%20the%20persistent%20challenges%20in%20vegetable%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAn%20organic%20journey%20leading%20to%20a%20patented%20grow%20bag%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyyo%20was%20first%20introduced%20to%20organic%20farming%20while%20still%20in%20Malabar%2C%20where%20he%20experimented%20with%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20determine%20what%20worked%20best%20for%20various%20crops.%20After%20relocating%20to%20Nedumkandam%2C%20he%20expanded%20his%20organic%20farming%20practices%20to%20include%20livestock.%20On%20his%20three-acre%20farm%2C%20cows%20and%20goats%20coexist%20with%20vegetables.%20He%20notes%20that%20cow%20dung%20serves%20as%20an%20excellent%20fertiliser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20like%20consuming%20the%20vegetables%20that%20were%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20Reading%20about%20the%20ill%20effects%20of%20consuming%20food%20with%20pesticides%20prompted%20me%20to%20start%20growing%20them%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Eyyo%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%