%3EEyyo%20prepares%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288760%2Fhow-to-grow-organic-ginger-in-grow-bags-and-sacks-kerala-farmer-shares-steps%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especial%20mix%20for%20his%20grow%20bags%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20starts%20by%20ploughing%20some%20topsoil%20and%20mixing%20in%20some%20lime%20powder%20(%3Cem%3Ekummayam%3C%2Fem%3E).%20He%20then%20leaves%20this%20mixture%20out%20in%20the%20sun%20for%2010%20days%2C%20regularly%20sprinkling%20water%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20he%20prepares%20another%20mixture%20using%20powdered%20cow%20dung%2C%20powdered%20bone%20meal%20(%3Cem%3Eellupodi%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20neem%20press%20cake%20(%3Cem%3Evep%20pinnakku%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20groundnut%20cake%20(%3Cem%3Ekadala%20pinnakku%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20trichoderma%2C%20and%20super%20phosphate%20or%20mussoorie%20phos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20mixture%20is%20stirred%20daily%20for%20six%20to%20seven%20days%2C%20with%20water%20added%20periodically.%20Finally%2C%20the%20two%20mixtures%20are%20combined%20and%20transferred%20to%20the%20grow%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grow%20bag%20is%20designed%20so%20that%20the%20mixture%20does%20not%20come%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20soil%20beneath%2C%20effectively%20preventing%20bacterial%20and%20fungal%20infections%20from%20spreading.%20Eyyo%20shares%20that%20this%20grow%20bag%20is%20patented%20and%20much%20more%20durable%20than%20standard%20ones%2C%20lasting%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20potentially%20even%20longer%20when%20used%20in%20home%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20bag%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20461px)%20100vw%2C%20461px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20